<refentry id="module-api-deleteInstance">

  <refnamediv>
    <refname>deleteInstance</refname>
    <refpurpose>deletes a module instance</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>

  <refsynopsisdiv> 
    <funcsynopsis>
      <funcprototype>
        <funcdef>void <function>deleteInstance</function></funcdef>
        <paramdef>void* <parameter>instance</parameter></paramdef>
      </funcprototype>
    </funcsynopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>

  <refsect1>
    <title>Description</title>

<para>To free the allocated module instance resources the engine calls <function>deleteInstance</function>. It must call this destructor after last usage of the module instance. The <parameter>instance</parameter> pointer is invalid after this call and may not be used for further calls.</para>

  </refsect1>

</refentry>